###

### 2. Ingrédient 1 - inclure aussi 2026 (doit retourner id=1, id=2, id=0, id=999)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Ingrédient 2 - 2024 (doit retourner id=3 et id=4)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/2/stockMovements?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Ingrédient 3 - 2024 (doit retourner id=5 et id=6)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/3/stockMovements?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Ingrédient 1 - seulement le 05 janvier 2024 (doit retourner id=1 uniquement, IN à 08h)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements?from=2024-01-05T00:00:00Z&to=2024-01-05T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Ingrédient 1 - seulement le 06 janvier 2024 (doit retourner id=2 uniquement, OUT à 12h)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements?from=2024-01-06T00:00:00Z&to=2024-01-06T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Ingrédient 1 - données 2026 seulement (doit retourner id=0 et id=999)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements?from=2026-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Ingrédient 1 - plage vide (futur, doit retourner [])
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements?from=2090-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2090-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Ingrédient 9999 - inexistant (doit retourner 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/9999/stockMovements?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. Ingrédient -1 - inexistant (doit retourner 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/-1/stockMovements?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2024-12-31T23:59:59Z
Accept: application/json

###

### POST - Ajouter des mouvements à l'ingrédient 1
POST http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "unit": "KG",
    "quantity": 3.5,
    "type": "IN"
  },
  {
    "unit": "KG",
    "quantity": 1.2,
    "type": "OUT"
  }
]

###

### POST - Ajouter un seul mouvement à l'ingrédient 2
POST http://localhost:8080/ingredients/2/stockMovements
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "unit": "L",
    "quantity": 5.0,
    "type": "IN"
  }
]

### POST - Ingrédient inexistant (doit retourner 404)
POST http://localhost:8080/ingredients/9999/stockMovements
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "unit": "KG",
    "quantity": 2.0,
    "type": "IN"
  }
]